The Yoruba Ronu Leadership Forum has hailed the decision by President Muhammadu Buhari to seek re election. In a statement by its Secretary General Akin Malaolu, the group said:  “Our trusted President to exercise his constitutionally right for second term in office should be commended and on this our group stands. ” We are happy for Nigeria and Nigerians the the glorious chapter and the intervention of APC into the affairs of our Nation shall further improved the quality of lives and most especially of our youths in the area of employment availability.
“Nigerians everywhere must see it as their duty to protect GOOD against EVIL which the oppositions connotes. “We shall on our part as a Group campaign faithfully for all contestants in APC regardless of tribes or religion” 